(317, 1, '2017-11-30 18:56:09', '2017-11-30 18:56:09', '<span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Come join us for a day of fun and excitement as we get ready to kick-off the What You Don\'t See campaign!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\">Fun activities for the whole family! Face painting, bounce house, water balloons, clowns, Daren the Lion, and much more!</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nGet ready for this monumental event as we kick off the What You Don\'t See campaign. You will have an opportunity to walk through and view the trailer, speak to drug abuse counselors, specialists, and officers, receive information about what you can do to spot the signs of drug abuse and participate in many other family friendly activities. Representatives from INOA will be present to provide information about their organization, what they\'re doing to combat drug abuse, as well as information on how to join. There will be food vendors, selling anything from hot dogs to walking tacos to pizza by the slice. Live music from The Nadas will finish off the night.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nDon\'t miss out on this one time opportunity to participate in something that will truly make a difference!', 'Kick-Off Event', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'kick-off-event', '', '', '2017-11-30 18:57:56', '2017-11-30 18:57:56', '', 0, 'http://renegaderaconteur.net/wordpress/finalProject/?post_type=tribe_events&#038;p=317', 0, 'tribe_events', '', 0),
