(686, 2, '2017-12-07 13:49:57', '2017-12-07 19:49:57', '&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: 24pt;\">LE Contact Tip Links</span></strong>\r\n\r\nDown below we have listed very informative websites that link up telephones lines you can dial to help someone as soon as possible.\r\n<blockquote><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">Since the start of </span><a style=\"text-indent: 0em;\" href=\"http://www.crimestoppersofcentraliowa.com/about.aspx\">Crime Stoppers of Central Iowa</a><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">, many calls have been received resulting in hundreds of arrests and recovery of substantial amounts of property. Calls have included information about murder, robbery, rape, assaults, drug and firearm offenses. Dial Today at: 515-223-1400</span></blockquote>\r\n<blockquote><a href=\"http://www.iccrimestoppers.org/report.php\">Iowa City Area CrimeStoppers</a> was established in July, 2007. The purpose of our organization is to prevent and reduce crime, by forming a partnership among the community, Law Enforcement, and the media. In doing so, we offer<strong>anonymity</strong>and<strong>cash rewards</strong>to anyone providing information leading to an arrest thereby making the community a safer place for all who live or work in the area.</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">Be the change you want to see in your community. Make sure you visit these websites to learn more.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'LE Tip Lines', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '148-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-07 13:49:57', '2017-12-07 19:49:57', '', 148, 'http://renegaderaconteur.net/wordpress/finalProject/?p=686', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
