lign: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"> Make sure</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">you visit these</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\">sites to learn more.</span></p>\r\n&nbsp;', 'LE Tip Lines', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '148-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-12-07 14:03:06', '2017-12-07 20:03:06', '', 148, 'http://renegaderaconteur.net/wordpress/finalProject/?p=701', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
